            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>To Silvanus Augustus, in honor of Lucius Titius Ismarus and in memory of Lucius Titius Epagathus, son of Hermetis, and Lucius Titius Epagathus senior.
                   Lucius Titius Onesimus, freedman of Ismarus, sexvir of Aquileia, gave this gift.
                </p>
